# UI and Design

## Colors

Use only semantic tokens from [design_guidelines.md](design_guidelines.md) and [tailwind.config.ts](tailwind.config.ts): `bg-background`, `bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-primary`, `text-destructive`, etc.

**NEVER use**: `bg-blue-500`, `text-red-600`, or `#...` in class names.

